  "text": "The test of coal sample permeability is carried out by using the three-axis gas seepage test system, and the test gas is nitrogen with a purity of 99.99%. The specific test conditions for the coal sample permeability are shown in tab. 1, and the specific method can be found in papers [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
